cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY 

This paper is about improving natural language processing using machine learning techniques, specifically by supplying it with external knowledge. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
